    p.
      MM.css is a minimal modern CSS Framework built upon <a href="http://sass-lang.com/" target="_blank">Sass</a>. Build fast, modern and mobile friendly sites without the bloat of JavaScript libraries.

    p.
      Primary goal of MM.css is to be a small size CSS library and yet provide enough styles and components for building a modern website.
      Licensed under <a href="#{site.github}blob/master/LICENSE.md" target="_blank">MIT license</a>, you are free to use this CSS framework for your personal as well as commercial projects.
    p.
      This site itself is built entirely with MM.css. No additional stylesheets are used.

